item.description: Join Cindi Lane as she introduces her series "Owning Your Magnificence" based on her newly published book "Owning Your Magnificence - A Spiritual Psychology." This series delves deeply into the psychology of seeing yourself for your light and not your lampshade. Bringing your fears to light and learning to love unconditionally we can become divine children again and begin to celebrate eachother for the magnificent, powerful and spiritual beings that we all are. During the series, Cindi will also hold a free book signing for anyone who purchases the book! Come with an open mind and be ready to see you inner light shine!
